Reffo — Licensing Overview

This repository is a monorepo containing multiple projects, each with its
own license:

  pelagora               AGPL-3.0-only   See pelagora/LICENSE
  pelagora-cli-installer AGPL-3.0-only   See pelagora-cli-installer/LICENSE
  pim-protocol           CC0-1.0         See pim-protocol/LICENSE
  reffo-webapp           Proprietary     No license granted

Unless otherwise noted, each project's license applies to all files within
its directory. Files outside of a specific project directory (e.g. root
config files, CI workflows) are not independently licensed and are provided
for repository maintenance purposes only.

For questions about licensing or commercial use, contact legal@reffo.ai.
